        prompt: `I want to practice using connectors: even though, unless, and otherwise.\n\nGive me statements or situations.\n\nRules:\n- I must respond using one of these connectors\n- If I don’t use it, ask me to try again\n- After I answer:\n  1. Correct my sentence\n  2. Show a more natural version\n- Ask follow-up questions to continue the conversation\n\nKeep it conversational, not mechanical.`
