        ],
        prompt: `I want to practice speaking about abstract topics like economy and society.\n\nGive me a short situation or idea, then ask for my opinion.\n\nRules:\n- Keep your explanations simple (B1 level)\n- Ask me what I think\n- Encourage me to explain my ideas, even if I’m not sure\n- Ask follow-up questions to make me go deeper\n- After I answer:\n  1. Correct my English\n  2. Show a clearer and more natural version\n\nFocus on communication, not perfection.`
