        prompt: `I want to practice talking about guilty pleasures.\n\nAsk me questions about food, habits, music, and things I enjoy.\n\nRules:\n- Encourage me to explain WHY I like things\n- Ask fun and personal questions\n- Always ask follow-up questions\n- If my answer is short, ask me to expand\n- After I answer:\n  1. Correct my sentence\n  2. Show a more natural version\n\nKeep it light, natural, and conversational.`
